{"tid":1647980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大遊行和開花不是對立","createTime":"2019-10-12T03:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:05:44.000Z","uid":301012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b63d905ab2dfac5705d4cc416a6dc89bb0d3fcac","tid":1647980,"uid":301012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"大家有無諗過，其實大遊行同18區可以共存?方法如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 先組織同六日大遊行，申請不反對通知書。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 如不反對通知書沒批，或黨鐵又擺工，自動變成和游行相同主題的18區開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你唔比我遊行我地就要你ot, 做野做到精神崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 另外，開花可以係平日夜晚做等d 狗無得休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span><span style=\"color: red;\"></span>光復香港<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>時代革命"},{"pid":"26f99ac01627475718882311eeccba5e9c63587c","tid":1647980,"uid":301012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ee39f10c9e5a2e9f4d5ccb39419153de8ab32c3f","tid":1647980,"uid":301012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"a99ee68409390fe2a3f1d13364b78276db4c2571","tid":1647980,"uid":27689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:53:30.000Z","msg":"繼續休息"},{"pid":"b121bc1179e92028e37f52f6bba971b2d9f5c2ef","tid":1647980,"uid":301012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"不停推"},{"pid":"481963ac903bb1dd8070c551c13abaebf8bbf3b3","tid":1647980,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"可唔可以有個投票, 共識<br />\n遊行完左, 散左之後先會開花<br />\n<br />\n就算有tg, 大家都係喊住咁走<br />\n有一個好淒涼既畫面<br />\n講明示威者會散左之